NetShield - Comprehensive Network Security Suite for OPNsense

Features:
- Application Identification: Detect and control 50+ applications via SNI/domain analysis
- Per-App/Device/VLAN/Network Blocking: Granular policy engine with scheduling
- DNS Filtering: Unbound-based domain blocking with safe search enforcement
- Web Category Blocking: 60+ content categories with custom overrides
- VPN/Proxy Detection: Detect and block unauthorized VPN, proxy, and tunnel usage
- Device Tracking: Auto-discover and manage network devices via ARP/DHCP
- GeoIP Blocking: Block traffic by country using MaxMind databases
- Custom Target Lists: Import and sync external blocklists
- Real-time Dashboard: Live statistics, alerts, and management interface
- Threat Intelligence: Suricata IDS/IPS integration with alert correlation
- DoH/DoT Bypass Prevention: Block DNS-over-HTTPS bypass attempts

All blocking is enforced via Unbound DNS + pf firewall rules.
No outbound telemetry or phone-home functionality.

